Images: ["[630_360_16804...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/thumb_files/630_360_1680436590-824.jpg)", "[1680436504-52...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680436504-526.jpg)"]

Tags: None

